cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation methods and word embeddings. The paper also involves linear maps and non-linear behavior, which are common topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper may also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as word embeddings are often used in natural language processing tasks related to image and video analysis. Finally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with non-linear behavior and neural networks are often used in machine translation tasks.
